Package: taxreftool
Title: Tools for Building Taxonomic Reference Databases
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Marko Suokas <your.email@example.com>
Description: This package offers utilities to create formatted FASTA and taxonomy
 files from raw UNITE and SILVA releases. It includes steps for parsing taxonomic
 strings, cleaning problematic annotations (e.g., 'uncultured', 'Incertae Sedis'),
 and validating species names, ensuring high-quality reference data for microbial
 community analysis.
